The,DataSift,Websocket,Streaming,API,allows,you,to,subscribe,to,DataSift,streams,using,Websockets,WebSockets,is,a,transmission,protocol,designed,to,permit,bi,directional,message,passing,over,TCP,connections,using,a,single,port,This,enables,browsers,to,connect,to,a,WebSocket,and,retrieve,curated,DataSift,content,in,near,realtime,without,the,technical,boundaries,of,an,HTTP,Stream,DataSift,provides,real,time,human,generated,data,including,social,data,blogs,and,news,data